      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONE KNEE NONI (2) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish half a length away in second (17.04) behind PAINT THE FENCE at this track. Good form should continue. AUDACIOUS DODGE (4) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (17.11) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 at this track last time out. Well placed here and can atone this time. SON OF SYBIL (1) goes very well this trip starting 15 times for five wins and three minors. Comes off a (19.69) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. FIREBIRD FLYER (6) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
